{"lastModified":1764145465781,"uri":"c::8275378522::vessel::b44670d0-79b9-11ee-8c61-3d799f112022","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Summer/Winter Operating Area: Caribbean Virgin Islands (United States/British Virgin Islands), Caribbean Virgin Islands (United States), Caribbean Virgin Islands (British Virgin Islands)\n\n\"Indulgence\" evokes pure pleasure—a surrender to comfort, beauty, and unforgettable moments. This stunning 2023 67’ Fountaine Pajot Alegria is designed for the ultimate luxury charter, accommodating up to 10 guests in four queen cabins and one bunk cabin, each with a private en-suite bathroom.\n\nUnwind in the forward jacuzzi, enjoy panoramic views from the 37-square-meter flybridge, or relax in the elegant 39-square-meter saloon, perfect for both dining and lounging. With a performance rig for smooth sailing, Indulgence offers the perfect blend of adventure and tranquility. Her sleek design and open layout create an atmosphere of effortless luxury, while the dedicated crew ensures every detail—from gourmet dining to personalized service—is tailored to you.\n\nLet Indulgence redefine your escape—where every sail is a memory in the making.","blueprint":{"name":"INDULGENCE","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::b44670d0-79b9-11ee-8c61-3d799f112022::assets::24602890-54ff-11ef-b2de-b1653664d96b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b44670d0-79b9-11ee-8c61-3d799f112022::assets::245f6540-54ff-11ef-82cb-656e5ab63e3f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b44670d0-79b9-11ee-8c61-3d799f112022::assets::2462e7b0-54ff-11ef-82cb-656e5ab63e3f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b44670d0-79b9-11ee-8c61-3d799f112022::assets::245d9081-54ff-11ef-82cb-656e5ab63e3f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b44670d0-79b9-11ee-8c61-3d799f112022::assets::24609dc0-54ff-11ef-82cb-656e5ab63e3f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::b44670d0-79b9-11ee-8c61-3d799f112022::assets::245c30f0-54ff-11ef-82cb-6